 auto;\r\n          max-width: 600px;\r\n        \"\r\n      >\r\n        <table\r\n          align=\"center\"\r\n          border=\"0\"\r\n          cellpadding=\"0\"\r\n          cellspacing=\"0\"\r\n          role=\"presentation\"\r\n          style=\"background: #ffffff; background-color: #ffffff; width: 100%\"\r\n        >\r\n          <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n              <td\r\n                style=\"\r\n                  direction: ltr;\r\n                  font-size: 0px;\r\n                  padding: 20px 0;\r\n                  text-align: center;\r\n                  vertical-align: top;\r\n                \"\r\n              >\r\n                <!--[if mso | IE]><table role=\"presentation\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:top;width:600px;\" ><![endif]-->\r\n                <div\r\n                  class=\"mj-column-per-100 outlook-group-fix\"\r\n                  style=\"\r\n                    font-size: 13px;\r\n                    text-align: left;\r\n                    direction: ltr;\r\n                    display: inline-block;\r\n                    vertical-align: top;\r\n                    width: 100%;\r\n                  \"\r\n                >\r\n                  <table\r\n                    border=\"0\"\r\n                    cellpadding=\"0\"\r\n                    cellspacing=\"0\"\r\n                    role=\"presentation\"\r\n                    style=\"vertical-align: top\"\r\n                    width=\"100%\"\r\n                  >\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                      <td\r\n                        align=\"left\"\r\n                        style=\"\r\n                          font-size: 0px;\r\n                          padding: 10px 25px;\r\n                          word-break: break-word;\r\n                        \"\r\n                      >\r\n                        <table\r\n                          border=\"0\"\r\n                          cellpadding=\"0\"\r\n                          cellspacing=\"0\"\r\n                          role=\"presentation\"\r\n                          style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px\"\r\n                        >\r\n                          <tbody>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                              <td style=\"width: 24px\">\r\n                                <img\r\n                                  alt=\"xAI logo\"\r\n                                  height=\"auto\"\r\n                                  src=\"https://data.x.ai/xai-logo.png\"\r\n                                  style=\"\r\n                                    border: 0;\r\n                                    display: block;\r\n                                    outline: none;\r\n                                    text-decoration: none;\r\n                                    height: auto;\r\n                                    width: 100%;\r\n                                  \"\r\n                                  width=\"24\"\r\n                                />\r\n                              </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                          </tbody>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                      </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                      <td\r\n                        align=\"left\"\r\n                        style=\"\r\n                          font-size: 0px;\r\n                          padding: 10px 25px;\r\n                          padding-top: 24px;\r\n                          padding-bottom: 24px;\r\n                          word-break: break-word;\r\n                        \"\r\n                      >\r\n                        <div\r\n                          style=\"\r\n                            font-family:\r\n                              -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont;\r\n                            font-size: 15px;\r\n                            font-weight: 300;\r\n                            line-height: 24px;\r\n                            text-align: left;\r\n                            color: #333333;\r\n                          \"\r\n                        >\r\n                          <h2>Grok 4.3 Non-Reasoning Launch and xAI API Model Retirement</h2>\r\n<p>Dear xAI API customers,</p>\r\n<p>We're excited to launch <strong>Grok 4.3</strong>, our latest flagship that leads the industry in agentic tool calling, instruction following, and non-hallucination rate. With a 1M token context window, it's our first model with configurable reasoning effort, including a new <a href=\"https://docs.x.ai/developers/model-capabilities/text/reasoning#effort-levels\">non-reasoning</a> mode for your most latency-sensitive use cases.</p>\r\n<p>To focus on this newest generation, we are retiring several earlier models effective May 15, 2026 at 12:00 PM PT:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><code>grok-4-1-fast-reasoning</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-4-1-fast-non-reasoning</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-4-fast-reasoning</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-4-fast-non-reasoning</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-4-0709</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-code-fast-1</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-3</code></li>\r\n<li><code>grok-imagine-image-pro</code></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Important</strong>\r\nThe deprecated model slugs will continue to work after the retirement date. Requests to these models will automatically redirect as follows:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Deprecated reasoning models → <code>grok-4.3</code> with <code>low</code> reasoning effort</li>\r\n<li>Deprecated non-reasoning models → <code>grok-4.3</code> with <code>none</code> reasoning effort</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Please note that requests to retired model slugs will be charged at the standard Grok 4.3 pricing of $1.25 / 1m tokens in and $2.50 / 1m tokens out. For additional details, please see our <a href=\"https://docs.x.ai/developers/migration/may-15-retirement\">May 15 Model Retirement Guide</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Try Grok 4.3 via our <a href=\"https://console.x.ai/team/default/chat-playground\">Chat Playground</a>. Thank you for building with Grok!</p>\r\n\r\n                        </div>\r\n                      </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                      <td\r\n                        align=\"left\"\r\n                        style=\"\r\n                          font-size: 0px;\r\n                          padding: 10px 25px;\r\n                          word-break: break-word;\r\n                        \"\r\n                      >\r\n                        <div\r\n                          style=\"\r\n                            font-family:\r\n                              -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont;\r\n                            font-size: 15px;\r\n                            font-weight: 300;\r\n                            line-height: 24px;\r\n                            text-align: left;\r\n                            color: #333333;\r\n                          \"\r\n                        >\r\n                          So long, and thanks for all the fish,<br />\r\n                          <strong>The xAI Team</strong>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                      </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                      <td\r\n                        style=\"\r\n                          font-size: 0px;\r\n                          padding: 10px 25px;\r\n                          word-break: break-word;\r\n                        \"\r\n                      >\r\n                        <p\r\n                          style=\"\r\n                            border-top: solid 1px #e8e8e8;\r\n                            font-size: 1;\r\n                            margin: 0px auto;\r\n                            width: 100%;\r\n                          \"\r\n                        ></p>\r\n                        <!--[if mso |